abb1b1e3aed0","tid":2175403,"uid":194370,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"5d83e66a7cce5427dd31d741b891181bdbec5db4","tid":2175403,"uid":233327,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T13:27:14.000Z","msg":"不過利物浦狗竇d人都算清醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T20:43:57.000Z","msg":"利狗賤種開作為利我又唔否認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n特別係facebook嗰班股東<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係以為垃圾利係霸主level<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n周圍出去串柒柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw講返張圖<br />\nEcho不嬲都係賤到仆街，我哋叫佢黨報<br />\n因為佢哋同比垃圾班主直接操控冇分別<br />\n用埋晒啲極低質banter以為自己有幽默感，要圍內同低質讀者一齊精神自瀆<br />\n實質係完全唔識尊重人，on9當有趣<br />\n美斯post 亦然，上次werner睇手機比echo班賤種<br />\n串話佢後悔冇跟高普亦然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但明明就係垃圾fsg有負於人人哋已經去利市搵埋屋，一下就話自己冇錢買佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無仇無怨周圍得罪人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n作為利狗，大把人極之討厭Echo呢份黨報同班傻鳩股東淨係識吹奏班主唯穩同歪曲事實，仲要以為自己真係好撚勁嗰下先乞人憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有呢班人代表利狗，俾人笑都唔抵可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbdb41eac5e615fc484fc10f32a4e42543d79e77","tid":2175403,"uid":209773,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T21:00:21.000Z","msg":"贏你4-0串吓有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁就賤種？<br />\n<br />\n而家美斯轉會姐，你話如果美斯斷腳收山，利迷再po呢張相話good luck咁就真係賤種喇<br />\n<br />\n咁都話賤種嘅話，BR Football呢啲抽水channel仲賤啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樓主反利都俾個好啲嘅point"},{"pid":"361fb5776975fbd8b8e7a715c03073c3f1fc12b5","tid":2175403,"uid":194370,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"bbdb41eac5e615fc484fc10f32a4e42543d79e77","tid":2175403,"uid":209773,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T21:00:21.000Z","msg":"贏你4-0串吓有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁就賤種？<br />\n<br />\n而家美斯轉會姐，你話如果美斯斷腳收山，利迷再po呢張相話good luck咁就真係賤種喇<br />\n<br />\n咁都話賤種嘅話，BR Football呢啲抽水channel仲賤啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樓主反利都俾個好啲嘅point"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T21:16:52.000Z","msg":"係咪盲反利都可以商榷，樓主如果要講標題同內容就應該要一致，即係specific ECHO呢單野上係賤種 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要反利亦都應該逐個論點提出黎，唔係打稻草人就算<br />\n<br />\n但你知我知ECHO賤種真係唔係第一日嘅事喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無啦啦，又搞werner,又串鳩哥狗，又串小花，仲要出文屌自己球迷<br />\n佢哋係一個正式嘅報社，唔係求其clickbait content farm page，呢種咁低質嘅banter 我係利都接受唔到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲覺得好尷尬好羞恥添<br />\n<br />\n不過公道講番句，呢個post都係一個低質素嘅banter <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}